00:00:30.497 --> 00:00:31.698 line:5%,start
No, no, no. No, no, no.

00:00:31.931 --> 00:00:32.999 line:5%,start
She's threatened by me.

00:00:33.466 --> 00:00:35.802 line:5%,start
NARRATOR: Coming up on
