00:00:50.617 --> 00:00:52.786 line:5%,start
I don't want her to
have these experiences.

00:00:52.852 --> 00:00:55.288 line:5%,start
I don't want people to think
it's all about the screaming.

00:00:55.355 --> 00:00:56.923 line:5%,start
Where were you guys three years ago?

00:00:56.990 --> 00:00:58.892 line:5%,start
Crap like you should
be shoved down a toilet.

00:00:58.958 --> 00:01:00.894 line:5%,start
We beat you, so that's how crappy I am.

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:02.862 line:5%,start
Look at your poor
pathetic mother over there.

00:01:02.929 --> 00:01:04.564 line:5%,start
Did you just call my mother pathetic?

00:01:04.631 --> 00:01:05.799 line:5%,start
I don't care.

